{
  "lines": [
    {
      "character": "Player",
      "text": "王座大厅... 最后的禁地。",
      "expression": "normal"
    },
    {
      "character": "Onyx",
      "text": "我亲爱的兄弟... 你终于走到了这里。",
      "expression": "dark"
    },
    {
      "character": "Onyx",
      "text": "我是你的团长，黑曜。曾经的圣剑骑士团领袖。",
      "expression": "dark"
    },
    {
      "character": "Player",
      "text": "团长... 你为什么要背叛骑士团？",
      "expression": "sad"
    },
    {
      "character": "Onyx",
      "text": "背叛？我是为了拯救它！",
      "expression": "determined"
    },
    {
      "character": "Onyx",
      "text": "圣物腐化了我们的心，让我看着兄弟相残。",
      "expression": "sad"
    },
    {
      "character": "Onyx",
      "text": "我偷走碎片，是为了结束这一切！",
      "expression": "determined"
    },
    {
      "character": "Onyx",
      "text": "但你也来了。带着你所谓的「拯救」。",
      "expression": "dark"
    },
    {
      "character": "Onyx",
      "text": "兄弟，今天只有一个能活着离开。",
      "expression": "determined"
    }
  ]
}